name: Debug
body:
### Debug

Files:

README.md : this file
LICENSE : please read it
examples.php : included just as a sample of usage
print_d.php : a file of static functions which can be called independently
printer.php : a singleton class used by print_d, or can be used directly
backtrace.php : backtrace information class
builder.php : builds the debug string information
timer.php : keeps track of the time
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
